    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 小生物也能改变世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 作为一个刚踏上岛屿的冒险家，你的任务是追寻腐化的源头。然而，一只调皮的苍鹭抢走了你的喷水枪，飞进了被腐化吞噬的狂野森林。现在，冒险正式开始</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284200/extras/6b45a8c187a4303d3740e5dc2a0ea79f.poster.avif?t=1772204695\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284200/extras/6b45a8c187a4303d3740e5dc2a0ea79f.webm?t=1772204695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284200/extras/6b45a8c187a4303d3740e5dc2a0ea79f.mp4?t=1772204695\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 探索充满未知的森林</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 深入狂野森林，踏上夺回喷水枪的旅程。途中，你将遇见各种奇妙的小动物，揭开森林深处的秘密。岛上不仅有丰富多样的自然景观，还有隐藏的神秘遗迹等待你去发现。追踪腐化的过程充满挑战，但你注定会完成这个使命！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284200/extras/b31b9f5e0065e7ef4685e7163fa7b1c3.poster.avif?t=1772204695\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284200/extras/b31b9f5e0065e7ef4685e7163fa7b1c3.webm?t=1772204695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284200/extras/b31b9f5e0065e7ef4685e7163fa7b1c3.mp4?t=1772204695\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 用智慧和行动解开谜题</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 利用喷水枪的不同模式清理环境，或者用你灵巧的爪子解决难题，为冒险开辟道路。无论是清理障碍还是破解机关，每一步都将带你更接近苍鹭和腐化的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284200/extras/986b958fc7e215de08206f949921e902.poster.avif?t=1772204695\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284200/extras/986b958fc7e215de08206f949921e902.webm?t=1772204695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284200/extras/986b958fc7e215de08206f949921e902.mp4?t=1772204695\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 重塑森林的生机</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 随着腐化被净化，森林逐渐恢复生机，曾经的美好景象再度浮现。看着森林重新焕发生机，你一定会感到无比满足与喜悦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284200/extras/c14f7d8518bd3de39f8b7af07e8c0a2d.poster.avif?t=1772204695\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284200/extras/c14f7d8518bd3de39f8b7af07e8c0a2d.webm?t=1772204695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284200/extras/c14f7d8518bd3de39f8b7af07e8c0a2d.mp4?t=1772204695\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
